---
title: Apricot-Glazed Salmon & Roast Potatoes with Almond, Radish & Feta Salad
description: Elevate your dining experience with our exquisite apricot-glazed salmon, featuring succulent salmon fillets glazed to perfection in a citrusy sauce. Accompanied by crispy roast potatoes and a fresh, crunchy salad, this harmonious trio promises a symphony of textures and flavours that will leave your palate delighted and satisfied.
